oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: "This Is Your Life" parody - Noble-Dury Advertising Agency - Part 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part 1 of a parody of radio show "This Is Your Life", in which the subject of the show is Albert Noble, of Noble-Dury Advertising Agency. The voice of Ralph Edwards is parodied by T. Tommy Cutrer, according to information written on sleeve. Other voices are parodied by unidentified male and female speakers.
